Entries.default: "Been out to sea for months. Nice to be on land a while."
"If you're sailing these waters, you'll want to see Sanza about a map."
"Looks like your ship needs some work. I'd talk to Zamar."
"There are riches to be made on more distant shores than these."
"It takes an adventuring spirit to succeed in Deadfire."
"A good shantey helps to pass the time at sea."
